Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不想忘却的回忆吗


